{
  "stem": "9943.1",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "But my father at that time insisted that I wouldn't go on Saturday.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And they thought, maybe, I was a rabbi's daughter or something like that.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "But nobody was teasing me, nothing.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "Just it was a strange world.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "An interesting world, but a strange world.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Well, that's how I was exposed to it.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I, I, I didn't see-- I didn't see others standing.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So--",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, pretty soon--",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Pretty soon-- pretty soon, I was a very good pupil.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And people treated me well.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And, and I was not-- I don't remember anything, except that it was like entering a world that you had very little knowledge of.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] In, in the, the house where we lived, there were a lot of-- it was a big house.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And there were a lot of tenants.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And we pretty soon started to know the children there and played together.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "But as I said, that's when I started to hear the teasing of Jews and, well, entered into my life, let us say, much more an understanding of a Jewish girl in a non-Jewish world.",
      "word_count": 35
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "But--",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Pardon me?",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, a year later-- and I cannot even say exactly.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Because I went myself to that school.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Another school that I-- after I jumped over the classes, I mean, I studied in summertime and had to change a school in order to enter a higher grade where-- [INAUDIBLE] some Jewish girls there in that-- in those schools.",
      "word_count": 40
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And then one of my sisters, Sarah, was going to the same school beside it.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And subsequently, I cannot tell you much about their schooling.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I can say much more about my own.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "But again, I, I, I wouldn't be able to go in any details about what, what happened to them.",
      "word_count": 19
    }
  ],
